                              SRS Documentation on library login 
                                      Introduction
this website is used to provide the information on the books available and user login with faster reservation

          Overview:
Scope: mainly provides a faster searching and reservation of books with a easy user interface.

Objective : to perform a easy user login on reservation of books on fixed time

Features:
      1) easy user interface
      2) faster search
      3) Scalability

Functional Requirements : server connectivity
                          data collection on books
                          reservation on books

Non Functional requirements : Dashboard
                              user login form
                              tool section 
